37214>>>>>    
37214>>>>>    //
37214>>>>>    // This procedure is called when validating a session and after logging in. Its purpose is to 
37214>>>>>    // update properties based on the session and user data. Augment this function to update 
37214>>>>>    // properties based on the session / user table. Note that WebAppUser and WebAppSession contain
37214>>>>>    // the right records when this procedure is called.
37214>>>>>    //
37214>>>>>    // Params:
37214>>>>>    //      bClear   True if the procedure is called before session validation to clear properties.
37214>>>>>    //
37214>>>>>    Procedure UpdateSessionProperties Boolean bClear
37216>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37216>>>>>        
37216>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37217>>>>>        
37217>>>>>        //  Update user properties
37217>>>>>        If (not(bClear) and HasRecord(hoUserDD)) Begin
37219>>>>>            Set psUsername to (Trim(WebAppUser.FullName))
37220>>>>>            Set psLoginName to (Trim(WebAppUser.LoginName))
37221>>>>>            Set piUserRights to WebAppUser.Rights
37222>>>>>            
37222>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesSet 
37223>>>>>        End
37223>>>>>>
37223>>>>>        Else Begin
37224>>>>>            Set psUsername to ""
37225>>>>>            Set psLoginName to ""
37226>>>>>            Set piUserRights to 0
37227>>>>>            
37227>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesClear
37228>>>>>        End
37228>>>>>>
37228>>>>>    End_Procedure
37229>>>>>    
37229>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesSet
37231>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37231>>>>>    End_Procedure
37232>>>>>    
37232>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesClear
37234>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37234>>>>>    End_Procedure
37235>>>>>    
37235>>>>>    Procedure EndSession
37237>>>>>        Integer iErr
37237>>>>>        Boolean bLogWebSession
37237>>>>>        Handle hoSessionDD       
37237>>>>>        
37237>>>>>        Get phoSessionDD to hoSessionDD
37238>>>>>        Get pbLogWebSession to bLogWebSession
37239>>>>>        If not bLogWebSession Begin
37241>>>>>            Forward Send EndSession
37243>>>>>            Procedure_Return
37244>>>>>        End
37244>>>>>>
37244>>>>>            
37244>>>>>        //  Check if session exists
37244>>>>>        Send Clear of hoSessionDD
37245>>>>>        Get psSessionKey to WebAppSession.SessionKey
37246>>>>>        
37246>>>>>        Send Find of hoSessionDD EQ Index.1
37247>>>>>        If (Found) Begin
37249>>>>>            Set Field_Changed_Value of hoSessionDD Field WebAppSession.Active to "N"
37250>>>>>            Get Request_Validate of hoSessionDD to iErr
37251>>>>>            If (iErr) Begin
37253>>>>>                // this should not happen. If it does its a programming error
37253>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM C_$WebAppSessionValidateFailed
37254>>>>>>
37254>>>>>                Procedure_Return
37255>>>>>            End
37255>>>>>>
37255>>>>>            Send Request_Save of hoSessionDD
37256>>>>>        End
37256>>>>>>
37256>>>>>    End_Procedure
37257>>>>>
37257>>>>>End_Class
